{
  "text": "In [CITATION_1] future null infinity I + is constructed as a limiting ingoing null hypersurface emanating from spacelike infinity \u03b9 0 . More precisely, given an initial asymptotically flat spacelike hypersurface \u03a3 0 , we can define a family of null hypersurfaces C Figure 3 . Construction of coordinates near null infinity.",
